" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41gCBA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41gCBA2.jpg&h=ba05256d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1e4da5f806fc95b3289a83b0d8220a68b151c3b","tid":1526171,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n吹大雞每個站都黎個大清洗<br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明明你地有能力 又咁容易 點解大家仲未收狗鐵皮?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523278</a>"},{"pid":"934e6db1d9fb91b2eebdba8e4506b633fc7e16d1","tid":1526171,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:43:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f72171bf3ee1f5b78e05b060d2cd0fd1428519d5","tid":1526171,"uid":181939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:43:23.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"fa2e5bd8dd74e3b85d78ffb154bc8f60fb44855a","tid":1526171,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:43:31.000Z","msg":"E線 E11 E21 E22 E23 E22A E32 E42 就「一號及二號客運大樓」落 呢個係機場下層 可落車<br />\nE33 E34A E34B E33P就搭到總站<br />\nE41要T1落 轉接駁巴<br />\n所有A線搭到 機場（地面運輸中心）巴士總站"},{"pid":"2e4a734ff2ad35caa681706f6dfceec1281d754c","tid":1526171,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"96cf849736bb9793b8e9f5b7af2250fba9b9f1de","tid":1526171,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:43:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":